<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">(=E2=9E=97) How To Convert Teaspoons to Tabl=
espoons (tsp to tbsp)</h2>



<p>To convert teaspoons (tsp) to tablespoons (tbsp), simply divide the numb=
er of teaspoons by 3. This is because there are 3 teaspoons in 1 tablespoon=
.</p>



<p>Here=E2=80=99s the formula:</p>



<p><strong>tablespoons (tbsp) =3D teaspoons (tsp) =C3=B7 3</strong></p>



<p>For example, if you have 9 teaspoons and you want to convert them to tab=
lespoons, you would calculate:</p>



<p>9 teaspoons =C3=B7 3 =3D 3 tablespoons (tbsp)</p>



